    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-10-07T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-10-07T00:00:00-05:00" n="491"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d491">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">881.00/10–747: Airgram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Caffery</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-10-07">October 7,
                            1947</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_A1">A–1491</gloss>. Chauvel asked me today for luncheon with
                    General Juin who is here on a brief trip from Morocco. They both reiterated that
                    the French Government intends to proceed with democratic reform in Morocco. They
                    both insisted that the main obstacle in the way of these reforms is the Sultan
                    of Morocco who objects at every step to anything approaching democratic reform.
                    They both agreed that a time limit must be set for the establishing of
                    self-government in that country.</p>
                <p>General Juin plans to return to Morocco within eight days.</p>
                <closer>[<signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Caffery</hi>
                    </signed>]</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
